{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3962e216fb","title":"对《红旗》杂志评论员文章《无产阶级革命派联合起来》的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f6317e185d","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":14,"articleId":"3962e216fb"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[{"id":"4939e9bc7e","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"3962e216fb","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在中共中央政治局常委、中央文化革命小组组长、《红旗》杂志总编辑陈值达1967年1月14日送审的这篇文稿上。陈佰达送审时在文稿上写有：“王力和关锋两同志给《红旗》写了一篇评论，请顺阅！”王力、关锋，当时均任中共中央文化革命小组组员、《红旗》杂志副总编辑。《无产阶级革命派联合起来》一文，后以本刊评论员的名义在1967年1月16日出版的《红旗》杂志第二期上发表。这篇文章中引用了毛泽东的一段话：“从党内一小搬走资本主义道路当权派手里夺权，是在无产阶级专政条件下，一个阶级推翻一个阶级的革命，即无产阶级消灭资产阶级的革命。"}],"contents":[{"id":"da1cda7021","type":"title","text":"对《红旗》杂志评论员文章《无产阶级革命派联合起来》的批语！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"3962e216fb"},{"id":"4939e9bc7e","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"3962e216fb"},{"id":"83865469df","type":"paragraph","text":"写得很好。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"3962e216fb"},{"id":"675a052088","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"3962e216fb"},{"id":"9afcef40ce","type":"paragraph","text":"一月十四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"3962e216fb"}],"page":{"id":"256c9f196d","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"3962e216fb","start":272,"end":272}}}},"__N_SSG":true}